snippet.title: Are the New England Patriots legit contenders? | (debatable)
snippet.description:
Welcome back to (debatable)! On today’s show, Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and Mike Golic Jr. break down Week 10 of the NFL! Can the Patriots make a deep playoff run? How concerned should the Bucs be after losing to Washington? What’s the biggest takeaway from the Packers’ win against the Seahawks? Did Lincoln Riley make a mistake benching Caleb Williams? Plus, Cam Newton makes his Panthers return, Jarrett Allen welcomes Luka Garza to the NBA and the Chiefs look like the Chiefs again!

5:00 Are the New England Patriots legit contenders?
